Dear (older) Me 
Hi babe! Still kicking and breathing I presume, otherwise you wouldn't be reading this:) I hope I did a good enough job staying away from too much drinking and no smoking and you're not TOO wrinkly and aged alright. 
I hope you can look at me from this time of your/our life and can say out in confidence "Damn, I've come such a long way... Look how skinny I was and I complained about every bloody physicality flaw I could find on me" LOL 
Anyways keep going and you're doing good whatever you are doing. 
I love you.
-22yr old Shannon (Dec 2018)
